{"lemma":"رُخْصُ","slug":"رُخْصُ","root":"ر.خ.ص","root_slug":"ر-خ-ص","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-خ-ص","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n15124","n15130","n15131"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D9%8F%D8%AE%D9%92%D8%B5%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of رُخْصَة (ruḵṣa)","tags":["form-of","plural"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of رُخُصَة (ruḵuṣa)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n15124","headword_ar":"رَخُصَ","root":"rxS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruxoSN","text_ar":"رُخْصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing, Msb, or a price, S, A)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, cheap, low-priced,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"low."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb, K, TA.) [Accord. to all of these authorities, this seems to be the primary signification: but Et-Tebreezee (Ham p. 47) thinks it to be from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raxoSapN","text_ar":"رَخْصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a woman, as meaning “ soft, or tender. ”] Some say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raxaSa","text_ar":"رَخَصَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also; but this is not of established authority. (MF.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raxuSa","text_ar":"رَخُصَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, A, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raxaASapN","text_ar":"رَخَاصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruxuwSapN","text_ar":"رُخُوصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruxoSaAnu","text_ar":"رُخْصَانُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Lth, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing, K, or the body, S, Msb, or flesh, A)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, soft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tender;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, Msb, K, TA;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soft to the feel:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and in like manner"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raxuSato","text_ar":"رَخُصَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a girl: (A:) or, said of a woman, inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruxoSaAnN","text_ar":"رُخْصَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, soft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tender, and delicate,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thin, in her external skin:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and said of a woman's fingers,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they were,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, soft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tender:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but when said of a plant, inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raxaASapN","text_ar":"رَخَاصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, soft, flaccid,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"easily"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quickly broken:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth:) [and said of a twig, or rod,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, fresh,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"succulent, and soft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tender:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raxoSN","text_ar":"رَخْصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["M","A","Msb","K","S","Lth","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n15130","headword_ar":"رَخْصٌ","root":"rxS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a thing, (A, K,) or to the body, (S, Msb,) and to flesh, and to a plant, (A,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Soft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tender;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, Msb, K;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soft to the feel:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raxiySN","text_ar":"رَخِيصٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same, (AA, M, K,) applied to a garment, or piece of cloth, (AA, K,) as also the former: (TA:) fem. of each with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, TA:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raxoSpN","text_ar":"رَخْصةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also applied to a girl, (A,) and to a woman, (K, TA, but omitted in the CK,) and to fingers, signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not rigid"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tough:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or, applied to a woman, it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tender, and delicate,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thin, in her external skin:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and applied to a woman's fingers,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tender:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raxoSN","text_ar":"رَخْصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a plant,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soft, flaccid,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"easily"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quickly broken:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, TA:) and applied to a twig, or rod,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fresh,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"succulent, and soft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tender:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) the pl."},{"kind":"page_break","n":1059},{"kind":"text","text":"of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raxoSN","text_ar":"رَخْصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rixaASN","text_ar":"رِخَاصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) and that of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raxoSapN","text_ar":"رَخْصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raxaAy^iSu","text_ar":"رَخَايِصُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is irreg. [as such, but reg. as pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raxiySapN","text_ar":"رَخِيصَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (K, TA;) occurring in poetry. (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa raxoSu Aljasadi","text_ar":"هُوَ رَخْصُ الجَسَدِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is soft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tender, in body."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AimoraA^apN raxoSapu Albadani","text_ar":"اِمْرَاَةٌ رَخْصَةُ البَدَنِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A woman soft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tender, in body."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["A","K","S","Msb","AA","M","TA","Lth"]},{"entry_id":"n15131","headword_ar":"رُخْصٌ","root":"rxS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[see 1, of which it is the inf. n., in the first of the senses explained above. ―         -b2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"act of making cheap;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] a subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroxaSahu","text_ar":"اَرْخَصَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the first of the senses here assigned thereto. (Msb.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}